thread.title: Lydia Sawyer
thread.title_full: Ann Summers Ltd reviewed by Lydia Sawyer

author: Lydia Sawyer
title: Lydia Sawyer
text:
I have used the site many times and never had an issue. Ordered it friday night and I collected it from store on the Tuesday am. Can't fault the quick turn around.
The Jaime body which is what I ordered is good quality, well made and fits very well. The boyfriend was very happy!
